### Get my applied jobs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/applications/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get application by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/applications/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update application (re-apply)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/applications/1/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "resumeLink": "https://example.com/resume.pdf",
  "coverLetter": "Updated cover letter content"
}

###

### Update application status (admin/recruiter only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/applications/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "statusId": 2,
  "notes": "Promising candidate, moving to next round"
}

###

### Delete an application (only if not reviewed yet)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/applications/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
